        "TileImage": "$($repository bdc07512-8164-4d2c-9c20-1b54c00ae7ae).Image",
        "Description": "Having slain the Sgàil Dragon at the top of his magnificent castle, you take a moment to breathe as you bask in your victory.\r\rHowever, a gaggle of pilferers have stolen parts of the Sgàil Dragon&apos;s treasure without you looking. They&apos;ve dispersed themselves across the island in an attempt to flee.\r\rGrab your weapon, don your armor, and claim what&apos;s rightfully yours. Be sure to grab all the gold coins they drop before you leave!",
